Package: fabricQueryR
Title: Query Data in 'Microsoft Fabric'
Version: 0.2.1.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Luka",
             family = "Koning",
             role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
             email = "koningluka@gmail.com"),
      person(given = "Kennispunt Twente",
             role = "fnd",
             email = "info@kennispunttwente.nl"))
Description: 
    Discover workspaces, items, and workload endpoints in 'Microsoft Fabric'.
    Provides helpers to open parameterized 'DBI' connections to 'SQL' endpoints
    of 'Lakehouse', 'Data Warehouse', and 'SQL Database' items; submit
    'Data Analysis Expressions' ('DAX') queries to semantic model datasets in 'Microsoft
    Fabric' and 'Power BI'; read 'Delta Lake' tables stored in 'OneLake'
    ('Azure Data Lake Storage Gen2'); execute 'Kusto Query Language' ('KQL')
    queries against 'Eventhouse' databases; and execute 'Spark' code via the
    'Livy API'.
